nd providing a clear call-to-action.\n\n**Key Takeaways:**\n\n* Identify the top 5 automation mistakes that are killing businesses\n* Provide real-world examples of businesses that have successfully implemented automation strategies\n* Offer actionable advice and step-by-step guidance on how to fix these mistakes\n* Include a clear call-to-action, such as a free download or a consultation\n\nBy following this strategic alignment, we can create a high-performing video that resonates with the target audience, fills the competitor gaps, and achieves a high CPM.",
